#

Greek Salad

10 min
$10
200 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuick

Description

A refreshing and vibrant salad packed with fresh vegetables and feta cheese, drizzled with a tangy dressing.

Ingredients

  • cucumbers: 2, diced
  • tomatoes: 3, chopped
  • red onion: 1/2, thinly sliced
  • bell pepper (any color): 1, chopped
  • feta cheese: 1 cup, crumbled
  • olives (kalamata or green): 1/2 cup
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • dried oregano: 1 teaspoon
